{"tid":1578161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實英文一早1971年已經有一本大技能書+大魔法書：The Anarchist Cookbook","createTime":"2019-09-18T04:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T07:50:39.000Z","uid":131691,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb35a0d84b23a93429e4c926bdecc6de583fd0e","tid":1578161,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:56:02.000Z","msg":"真係乜都有教，火魔法只不過係其中一個<br />\n就算唔想用魔法嘅，都可以學到唔少技能，比如自衛嘅時候一啲基本嘅hand-to-hand combat技能<br />\n（第一章講毒品，大家可以skip，第二章講電訊竊聽，但係因爲本書太舊，好多呢part嘅資料已經過時）<br />\n<br />\n我見有一個Telegram channel 《香港革命指南》 喺度慢慢翻譯緊，暫時應該翻譯咗正確揸刀嘅教學： <a href=\"https://t.me/hkmanual\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmanual&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87EvjwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=98624b98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmanual</a><br />\n<br />\n全文嘅PDF喺Internet Archive搵到：<a href=\"https://archive.org/details/anarchist-cookbook-william-powell_201609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fanarchist-cookbook-william-powell_201609&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87EvjwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=19499b5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.org/details/anarchist-cookbook-william-powell_201609</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係個目錄，內容我就唔post啦：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CaSTXeT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCaSTXeT.png&h=2847b406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/osr158e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fosr158e.png&h=57f9998d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baa7c848d9a80db32bbbb2336e14093861324774","tid":1578161,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36315987a054f3af080270081a5fee03b65ab3f